# NAME: HonorOfKings_Direct
# AUTHOR: zijinan / ChatGPT
# DESC: Honor of Kings / Tencent domestic game DIRECT rule list migrated from the old plugin.
# SECURITY: Rule-only list. No plugin, no script, no rewrite, no MITM, no Host section, no server:system DNS override.
# USAGE: Add as Remote Rule with policy=DIRECT or policy=国内游戏策略.

